1
00:00:52,660 --> 00:00:54,910
Three hundred years ago,

2
00:00:57,290 --> 00:00:58,750
the human realm enjoyed peace.

3
00:00:58,750 --> 00:01:02,660
For centuries, the land was unharmed,

4
00:01:02,660 --> 00:01:04,720
and the people lived in tranquility.

5
00:01:05,660 --> 00:01:08,160
However, the sky split and the earth collapsed.

6
00:01:08,160 --> 00:01:10,330
The rift to the Demon Abyss opened wide,

7
00:01:10,330 --> 00:01:12,330
and towering mountains tumbled down.

8
00:01:12,330 --> 00:01:16,120
Demons surged into the human realm like a black tide.

9
00:01:16,450 --> 00:01:17,910
Wherever they went,

10
00:01:17,910 --> 00:01:19,660
the land was shattered,

11
00:01:19,660 --> 00:01:21,450
and lives were ruined.

12
00:01:21,700 --> 00:01:23,580
The people grieved,

13
00:01:23,700 --> 00:01:25,900
with millions of corpses lying around,

14
00:01:26,039 --> 00:01:27,910
and blood flowing like rivers.

15
00:01:28,580 --> 00:01:32,039
The human realm turned into a living hell.

16
00:01:32,750 --> 00:01:36,660
This was the catastrophe three hundred years ago.

17
00:02:37,660 --> 00:02:39,620
Mother, your son is unfilial.

18
00:02:40,450 --> 00:02:42,579
I can't take care of you in your old age.

19
00:02:44,290 --> 00:02:45,290
Stay alive.

20
00:02:45,700 --> 00:02:47,579
You must come back alive.

21
00:03:19,000 --> 00:03:20,000
Soldiers,

22
00:03:21,040 --> 00:03:24,540
lift your heads and look back.

23
00:03:30,870 --> 00:03:32,079
My son.

24
00:03:33,079 --> 00:03:35,620
There are your parents,

25
00:03:35,660 --> 00:03:37,260
and your wives and children.

26
00:03:37,620 --> 00:03:41,079
Behind us are the lights of thousands of homes.

27
00:03:41,620 --> 00:03:42,290
As long as we

28
00:03:42,290 --> 00:03:43,690
still have a breath left,

29
00:03:43,950 --> 00:03:47,370
we will never let the demons cross this pass.

30
00:03:58,250 --> 00:04:01,950
Tell me, are your swords

31
00:04:01,950 --> 00:04:03,000
sharp?

32
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:05,250
The land of Great Yong is still here.

33
00:04:05,370 --> 00:04:07,450
The sun, the moon, and the land are still here.

34
00:04:07,450 --> 00:04:09,700
The land of Great Yong is still here.

35
00:04:09,830 --> 00:04:12,040
The sun, the moon, and the land are still here.

36
00:04:12,040 --> 00:04:14,830
Kill!

37
00:05:01,080 --> 00:05:01,330
Du.

38
00:06:42,500 --> 00:06:43,580
I'll stall him

39
00:06:44,040 --> 00:06:45,200
to buy you time.

40
00:07:57,500 --> 00:07:59,370
Leave me alone.

41
00:08:00,500 --> 00:08:01,500
Keep going.

42
00:09:07,790 --> 00:09:09,370
I am willing to burn my soul

43
00:09:10,950 --> 00:09:13,080
and fall into endless reincarnation,

44
00:09:13,160 --> 00:09:15,090
in exchange for peace in this world

45
00:09:15,750 --> 00:09:18,830
and to meet you again in the next life.

46
00:09:24,660 --> 00:09:25,500
Sister.

47
00:09:26,660 --> 00:09:27,950
Ying,

48
00:09:27,950 --> 00:09:29,250
don't cry.

49
00:09:29,620 --> 00:09:30,830
Live well.

50
00:09:44,370 --> 00:09:45,830
Using my soul as a guide,

51
00:09:46,330 --> 00:09:49,200
I cast this blood pact for your reincarnations.

52
00:09:49,250 --> 00:09:50,370
You shall not fall in love.

53
00:09:50,370 --> 00:09:51,450
If you violate this pact,

54
00:09:51,450 --> 00:09:54,120
you shall never have a good end in all your lifetimes.
